{
  "texts": [
    "When it comes to setting the research tasks and interpreting the results, it is important to note that LLMs should not be seen as a source of facts.",
    "ChatGPT is designed to provide answers to user questions, but ChatGPT does not always produce factually accurate information.",
    "Because it does not differentiate between correct and incorrect information,",
    "ChatGPT merely compiles all information with no value judgment on its accuracy or precision.",
    "It also cannot produce new knowledge."
  ]
}